Grand Duchy of Silvervale
Overview
The Grand Duchy of Silvervale is one of the more prosperous and stable inland Grand Duchies. It is known for its beautiful temperate valleys, rolling hills, silver mines, and fertile farmlands. It maintains strong loyalty to the Kingdom of Vaelor while enjoying significant autonomy.

Ruler: Grand Duke Alaric Silvervale (Age 47, shrewd diplomat and competent administrator)
Capital: Moonford (Population: 89,000)
Total Population: 6.1 million
Economic Condition: Prosperous – Benefits from rich soil, silver mining, and safe internal trade routes.

Geography & Climate
Silvervale lies in the central-western heartlands of Veloria. The landscape is dominated by wide, gentle valleys, sparkling rivers, and forested hills. The climate is mild and temperate — warm summers, cool but rarely harsh winters, and frequent gentle rainfall that keeps the land lush and green. It is often called the “Silver Breadbasket” for its agricultural output.
